    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个section分别是\"Go to work\"和\"Go home\"。那每个section里大概有几个步骤？我需要预估一下布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
